quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,67,"Ni aŵala ŵati achitolaga ngakasamisangaga soni ŵangatenda ugagadi, nambo akasaŵa ŵakwimilichika chilikati cha yalakweyo."
  25,68,"Ni aŵala ŵangaakum’bendaga nnungu jwine pampepe ni Allah, soni ni ngaakuwulagaga mundu jwaakanyisye Allah (kum’bulaga) ikaŵeje paligongo lyakwitichika (ni malamusi ga Dini), nambo soni ŵangatenda chikululu. Sano jwachatende yele nikuti chasimangane ni ilagasyo (ya pa duniya)."
  25,69,"Ilagasyo tiikajonjechesyedwe kukwakwe lisiku lya Kiyama, ni chijukalonjele mwalakwemo aku juli jwakunyosyedwa."
  26,40,"“Kuti mwine uwwejo twakuye asaŵi naga ŵanganyao aŵe ŵakupunda.”"
  26,41,"Basi ndema jaŵaiche asaŵi ŵatite kwa Firiauna: “Ana chisimu kukwetu chikuŵe kwana malipilo (gambone) natuŵaga uwwejo ni ŵakupunda?”"
  26,42,"(Firiauna) jwatite: “Elo, konjechesya soni pelepo chisimu ŵanganyammwe pajele ndemajo chim’be mwa akuŵandichisyidwa (kukwangu).”"
  27,13,"Basi ndema jayaichilile isimosimo Yetu yakuloleka ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Awu ni usaŵi wakuonechela.”"
  27,14,"Ni ŵaikaaniile (isimosimoyo) mwalupuso nambo soni mwakulikwesya kutendaga mitima jao jaikulupilile kusyesyene. Basi nnole mujaŵelele mbesi ja akuwatanganya!"
  27,15,"Soni chisimu chene pamasile patwampele Daudi ni Sulaimana umanyilisi. Ni ŵatite ŵanaŵaŵili: “Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah Ajula jwaatulongwesye uwwe (pakutupa ukoto) kwapunda ŵajinji mwa achikapolo Ŵakwe ŵakulupilila.”"